# Concept Selection Template

## Below are the identified and prioritized objectives
1. No. of beats per minute.

2. Working of device.

3. Audio output.

4. Cost.



## PUGH Chart
|Objectives| Weightage| Designe Idea 1.|Designe Idea 2.|Designe Idea 3.|Designe Idea 4.|
|----------|----------|----------------|---------------|---------------|---------------|
|No. of beats per minute|6|Datum|-|+|-|
|Working of device|8|Datum|-|+|+|
|Audio output|7|Datum|-|+|-|
|Cost|5|Datum|+|-|-|
|+Score| | |5|21|8|
|-Score| | |-21|-5|-18|
|Total| | |-16|16|10|

The Best Concept selected is : **_Design Idea 3_**
***


## Justification:

|Design Idea No.|Objective|Score Given|Justification|
|---|--|--|--|
|**_2._**|Number of beats| -6|Beats will be less due to the presence of only one drumstick.|
| |Working of device|-8| Due to the complexity of the working of the device.|
| |Audio effect|-7|Sound produced is less because force produced by the stick on drum will be less.|
| |Cost|5| Since we are using less number of Servo motors i.e, only one.|
| |
|**_3._**|Number of beats| 6|Number of Beats will be more since we are using two drumsticks to make the beats.|
| |Working of device|8| Working of the device will be Easy because we are using directly servo motor because of which we can set precise angle.|
| |Audio effect|7|More sound is produced because two sticks are used to beat the drums.|
| |Cost|-5| Cost will be more because we are using two servo motors.|
| |
|**_4._**|Number of beats| -6|Number of Beats will be less because cam takes more time to make one complete revolution.|
| |Working of device|8| Easy working of the device because here we use only cam and holder.|
| |Audio effect|-7|Audio effect will be less due to less number of beats.|
| |Cost|-5| Cost will be more since we are using robot hand to hold the instrument. |



